{"tid":1976453,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梯間從後以尼龍繩勒頸嚇煞女街坊    彩虹邨居民自保：勿夜歸","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T11:07:18.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"107cd05ffcf789096efa80c9a5dafd2d62478519","tid":1976453,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZASo_V8.4Lqq_LbMu7g7HA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200417a150736.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZASo_V8.4Lqq_LbMu7g7HA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzUwO2g9NjAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200417a150736.jpg&h=6435e073&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】彩虹邨昨日傍晚發生梯間勒頸施襲案，一名35歲女街坊在金碧樓梯間，被一名持刀男子從後以尼龍繩勒頸施襲。因應事件，居民李小姐坦言擔心自身安全，多次呼籲大家都要小心。李小姐指，涉案男子在逃，感覺不太安全，由於對方似乎熟識邨內環境，她因而估計為邨民。而為求自保，日後會盡量不行後樓梯，也盡量不要夜歸，和最好找人作伴。<br />\n<br />\n而一對由1980起至今已在邨內居住40年的母女指，邨內治安一向「OK」，但指如今時勢不好，更要小心，也希望警方多加巡邏。"},{"pid":"ef2549d18f7cf2bf2c09b86af254115938b5c815","tid":1976453,"uid":298077,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:14:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">也希望警方多加巡邏</span></span>    哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a51bc052e88dd5862e9b0496c0a0dcd4865e5fe","tid":1976453,"uid":50888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"搞個一蚊雞保鑣計劃"},{"pid":"0a2b15f3aacd8cf3803ec49f619a8cc9fe2b2b4d","tid":1976453,"uid":165749,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"聽講彩虹邨好多狗宿舍，個色魔會唔會就係&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88cd89901037d403db236d2f55976deebd97e69a","tid":1976453,"uid":121197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quo